channel.title: Duping problem
channel.description:
Hey everyone, i have recently encountered some dupers on my server and i dont know if there is some new rsps hacker or something but i need help. I tried to ipban him but he just kept coming back so i closed down my server. im running a hybrid pvp v3 source which is a 317 server. need helm asap please!
thanks
